profile:
* SEE IT FOR YOURSELF !!!

* Our service would give you full satisfaction in a matter of hours with very affordable prices !!!

* Who we are?

We are a professional cleaning company with high equipped tools that make your house and office look like new again.

* We Offer
- Carpet Cleaning Shampoo and Steam
- Odour and Stain removal of all kinds
- Fast Drying method
- Upholstery Deep cleaning
- Mattress Deep cleaning
- Tile & Grout cleaning

Why is Carpet Cleaning so important?

It helps to remove dust mites, bacteria and other allergens, which ultimately helps your family breathe easier and reduces the risk of colds and other health problems!

Why is Tile and Grout Cleaning important?

Because without regular professional cleaning, the grout in between tiles will start to look black and dirty. Not only does this look bad, but it can also harbor bacteria that could give off offensive odors or even make you sick.

Helping Clients Increase Indoor Air Quality & Maintain Their Homes For Over 40 Years!

Established in 1953, Flying Dutchman Cleaning is a professional carpet and upholstery cleaning company that has been providing quality, guaranteed workmanship to Guelph, Ontario and the surrounding area for many successful years!

At Flying Dutchman Cleaning, we know that being invited into your home is all about trust. We consider ourselves humble guests in your home and as such, we respect your personal privacy and space. By working hard to establish your trust through an open and honest working relationship, we frequently turn first-time customers into life-long friends and clients!

“The key to proper cleaning is in the extraction of soil.  Our methods and state-of-the-art systems excel in doing just that!”
